<i>We have already found a way to defeat the enemy.</i>

41
00:03:05,180 --> 00:03:07,900
<i>And I have learned two moves just within today.</i>

42
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:11,000
<i>In a few days, I'm sure I'll be able to learn them all.</i>

43
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:16,319
<i>His Majesty said that as long as I use the sword techniques he taught me, I'd surely defeat you.</i>

44
