<i>Yesterday, Commander Yan rendered great service in rescuing me.</i>

45
00:03:22,219 --> 00:03:24,819
<i>Knowing to use perilla leaf juice to save me.</i>

46
00:03:24,819 --> 00:03:27,479
<i>What reward do you want?</i>

47
00:03:30,900 --> 00:03:34,059
Boss, what's wrong?

48
00:03:46,140 --> 00:03:47,328
Please rise.

49
00:03:47,328 --> 00:03:49,520
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thank you, Your Majesty.

50
00:03:50,460 --> 00:03:54,240
Your Majesty seldom visits the Thousand Feather Guards training grounds. Why the sudden visit today?

51
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:58,260
I heard there were assessments today, so I came specially to observe.

52
00:03:58,260 --> 00:04:00,200
Please, Your Majesty, as you please.

53
00:04:07,932 --> 00:04:12,150
<i>[Unyielding]</i>

54
00:04:15,539 --> 00:04:17,172
Come on.

55
00:05:14,460 --> 00:05:17,440
<i>Brother Yan, this move is awesome! What's it called?</i>

56
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:21,260
<i>The Nine Heroes Stab, the hardest move to break in the Falling Petals Sword Technique.</i>

57
00:05:21,260 --> 00:05:24,120
<i>Once launched, it's either death or injury for most people.</i>

58
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:26,940
<i>- Except for us of the Qin family.
- Why is that?</i>

59
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:30,300
<i>Because our Qin family has a hereditary technique to counter it.</i>

60
00:05:42,339 --> 00:05:44,439
- Boss!
- Boss!

61
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:48,380
Boss!

62
00:05:48,380 --> 00:05:50,420
- Boss!
- Boss!

63
00:05:50,420 --> 00:05:53,224
- How are you?
- Boss, are you okay?

64
00:06:03,419 --> 00:06:06,260
- A'Cheng, quickly take Commander Yan back.
- Yes.

65
00:06:06,260 --> 00:06:08,380
I'll go and call the imperial physician.

66
00:06:09,580 --> 00:06:12,480
Boss, careful.

67
00:06:21,940 --> 00:06:23,400
How did you get wounded so badly?

68
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:25,400
Here, let me tend to your wounds.

69
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:28,300
I dare not trouble Your Majesty. I'll wait for the imperial physician to take care of it.

70
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:31,900
Commander Yan, my safety is entirely in your hands.

71
00:06:31,900 --> 00:06:34,800
Let me see. Be careful not to injure any vital part.

72
00:06:43,820 --> 00:06:46,620
<i>How to break this? Teach me quickly.</i>

73
00:06:51,859 --> 00:06:55,140
<i>Brother Yan, what's wrong with you?</i>

74
00:06:55,779 --> 00:06:57,660
<i>Imperial physician.</i>

75
00:07:04,620 --> 00:07:10,060
Commander Yan, Imperial Physician Qu has arrived.

76
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:12,179
Greetings, Your Majesty.

77
00:07:12,179 --> 00:07:15,380
Your Majesty, Commander Yan's sword wound was, after all, caused by me.

78
00:07:15,380 --> 00:07:19,299
So, with me and Imperial Physician Qu here, you can rest assured.

79
00:07:22,020 --> 00:07:24,419
Report Commander Yan's injuries at any time.

80
00:07:24,419 --> 00:07:26,720
Yes, Your Majesty.

81
00:07:27,419 --> 00:07:29,144
Take good care of him.

82
00:07:36,460 --> 00:07:39,160
- I respectfully see off Your Majesty.
- I respectfully see off Your Majesty.

83
00:07:44,940 --> 00:07:47,580
Commander Yan's endurance is truly astonishing.

84
00:07:47,580 --> 00:07:50,559
This wound is quite deep.

85
00:07:50,559 --> 00:07:54,079
This medicine, Xiao Qiangzi,

86
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:57,180
then you shall change it for Commander Yan daily.

87
00:07:57,180 --> 00:07:58,990
Remember, three times a day.

88
00:07:58,999 --> 00:08:00,620
Three times a day. Got it!

89
00:08:00,620 --> 00:08:03,199
Good, thank you for your efforts.

90
00:08:06,060 --> 00:08:08,280
I'm sorry.

91
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:12,170
It's all my fault; I've caused your injury.

92
00:08:12,170 --> 00:08:15,236
Don't blame yourself, you have improved quickly.

93
00:08:15,236 --> 00:08:17,260
It was my underestimation.

94
00:08:18,979 --> 00:08:22,260
A'Cheng, you go ahead.

95
00:08:29,179 --> 00:08:33,360
Commander, with your martial skills, how could you lose to Xiao Qiangzi?

96
00:08:34,659 --> 00:08:39,039
Do you know what move he used to stab me?

97
00:08:39,648 --> 00:08:41,632
Nine Heroes Stab.

98
00:08:42,260 --> 00:08:45,652
When we were little, it was the one with the greatest lethality

99
00:08:45,652 --> 00:08:48,419
from the Falling Petals Sword Technique that I practiced with His Majesty.

100
00:08:48,419 --> 00:08:51,580
He deliberately taught this sword technique to Xiao Qiangzi,

101
00:08:51,580 --> 00:08:54,290
and wanted to test whether or not I was Qin Yan.

102
00:08:54,290 --> 00:08:55,840
Therefore, I had to lose.

103
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:59,980
His Majesty suspects you? What do we do now?

104
00:09:17,140 --> 00:09:21,220
Just now, he confirmed that I have no other scars on my chest.

105
00:09:21,220 --> 00:09:23,760
Hopefully, he won't suspect me any further.

106
00:09:34,220 --> 00:09:36,839
It turns out it's not him.

107
00:09:39,980 --> 00:09:42,800
Since it's not him,

108
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:45,560
why does he keep coming to my mind?

109
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:47,000
Your Majesty,

110
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:51,699
that is because you haven't been to see Her Majesty for a long time.

111
00:09:53,539 --> 00:09:55,800
You know who I am speaking of.

112
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:57,390
Your Majesty,

113
00:09:57,390 --> 00:10:02,170
he has been dead for 15 years.

114
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:06,060
<i>[The Orchid Fragrance Follows the Wind]
Duke Ding has committed fraud and deception.</i>

115
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:08,870
<i>Conspired rebellion and misled the country.</i>

116
00:10:08,870 --> 00:10:12,060
<i>The whole family is to be executed. Thus decreed.</i>

117
00:10:14,799 --> 00:10:19,520
Yes, it's been 15 years.

118
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:26,220
It was still I who personally affixed the imperial seal.

119
00:10:26,220 --> 00:10:30,419
Your Majesty, the affairs of that year weren't really your fault.

120
00:10:30,419 --> 00:10:34,319
You weren't in control of your destiny. About your Brother Yan…

121
00:10:34,319 --> 00:10:36,919
Your Majesty, I spoke out of turn.

122
00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:39,740
Your Majesty, forgive me.

123
00:10:39,740 --> 00:10:43,220
Enough, rise.

124
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:50,259
It's also good that it's not him.

125
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:54,760
If he really appears before me,

126
00:10:56,040 --> 00:10:59,220
I also don't know how to face him.

127
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:04,160
Let's go.

128
00:11:04,980 --> 00:11:06,608
Yes.

129
00:11:16,399 --> 00:11:19,980
A'Cheng, how's Boss?

130
00:11:19,980 --> 00:11:23,859
Xiao Qiangzi, you really went too far this time.

131
00:11:40,179 --> 00:11:41,944
What's wrong?

132
00:11:44,059 --> 00:11:46,800
Has the medicine been applied?

133
00:11:49,740 --> 00:11:53,559
I'm sorry, Commander Yan.

134
00:11:53,559 --> 00:11:56,740
I admit, I wanted to win too much.

135
00:11:56,740 --> 00:11:59,380
Because I want to stay in the Thousand Feather Guards.

136
00:11:59,380 --> 00:12:04,000
But I really didn't intend to hurt you.

137
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:06,659
I thought your martial arts were so good,

138
00:12:06,659 --> 00:12:09,320
that I would not be able to harm you.

139
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:12,539
<i>I'm sorry, I've used you once again.</i>

140
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:23,880
It's inevitable for martial artists to get some minor injuries.

141
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:26,220
Don't take it to heart.

142
00:12:26,220 --> 00:12:28,459
Rest assured; I have thought it all through.

143
00:12:28,459 --> 00:12:31,779
From today on, I'll take care of your life in every aspect.

144
00:12:31,779 --> 00:12:34,240
Until you have recovered from your injuries.

145
00:12:35,779 --> 00:12:38,380
Here, rest well.

146
00:12:46,059 --> 00:12:47,380
Then, you rest well.

147
00:12:47,380 --> 00:12:50,500
I'll be right outside, I'll appear whenever you need me.

148
00:12:58,519 --> 00:13:00,559
Speaking of Yan Changyun,

149
00:13:00,559 --> 00:13:03,199
he's the sort of person who feels at a loss if he doesn't take advantage.

150
00:13:03,199 --> 00:13:06,120
What if Xiao Qiangzi doesn't agree to it?

151
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:08,839
I would get scolded by him once again.

152
00:13:08,839 --> 00:13:10,520
Maybe we should just forget it.

153
00:13:10,520 --> 00:13:11,699
Your Majesty is right.

154
00:13:11,699 --> 00:13:14,300
It's really not worth getting scolded over Xiao Qiangzi.

155
00:13:14,300 --> 00:13:16,156
Let's go back.

156
00:13:20,579 --> 00:13:22,920
After all, I'm the head of the harem.

157
00:13:22,920 --> 00:13:24,844
He is just a minor commander.

158
00:13:24,844 --> 00:13:28,260
He must give me the person I want, whether he wants to or not.

159
00:13:28,260 --> 00:13:30,800
Your Majesty, perhaps you should think it over.

160
00:13:30,800 --> 00:13:32,580
That Yan Changyun is quite frightening.

161
00:13:32,580 --> 00:13:34,412
Even Grand Empress Dowager dares not provoke him.

162
00:13:34,412 --> 00:13:36,536
- If you force the issue…
- I don't care.

163
00:13:36,536 --> 00:13:40,219
The earlier Xiao Qiangzi is by my side, the earlier I can keep His Majesty by my side.

164
00:13:40,219 --> 00:13:43,024
So that, I can bear an imperial heir sooner.

165
00:13:43,024 --> 00:13:44,679
- But…
- There are no buts.

166
00:13:44,679 --> 00:13:48,880
Today, even if I have to break heads and bleed, I must get Xiao Qiangzi.

167
00:13:50,656 --> 00:13:53,572
Boss, you haven't given me the new list of arrests.

168
00:14:05,620 --> 00:14:09,380
Boss, what's been with you lately? Is it because of Xiao Qiangzi?

169
00:14:09,380 --> 00:14:11,859
Did he leave you with some kind of psychological trauma?

170
00:14:14,819 --> 00:14:16,320
I did say that this person should not stay.

171
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:18,960
Let's just go all in on this.

172
00:14:19,639 --> 00:14:21,372
Greetings, Your Majesty.

173
00:14:21,372 --> 00:14:22,459
You may leave first.

174
00:14:22,459 --> 00:14:24,048
Yes.

175
00:14:26,884 --> 00:14:29,079
- Your humble servant pays respect to Her Majesty.
- Commander Yan, please, no need for formalities.

176
00:14:29,079 --> 00:14:30,160
Have a seat.

177
00:14:30,160 --> 00:14:33,184
Thank you, Your Majesty. Please, go ahead

178
00:14:39,179 --> 00:14:41,780
Your Majesty, your coming here must be for an important matter.

179
00:14:41,780 --> 00:14:44,559
I heard that Commander Yan has been injured.

180
00:14:44,559 --> 00:14:46,700
So, I came especially to pay a visit.

181
00:14:46,700 --> 00:14:50,460
And also, I have a small favor to ask incidentally.

182
00:14:50,460 --> 00:14:52,860
You needn't be polite, Her Majesty. Please give your command.

183
00:14:52,860 --> 00:14:54,499
Her Majesty's palace is short-staffed.

184
00:14:54,499 --> 00:14:57,559
We've come to ask Commander Yan for someone to be dispatched for use.

185
00:14:57,559 --> 00:15:01,159
Commander Yan, I know the business of the Thousand Feather Guards is busy.

186
00:15:01,159 --> 00:15:05,480
But this matter for Commander Yan was specially arranged by His Majesty himself.

187
00:15:07,819 --> 00:15:09,559
Your servant obeys the decree.

188
00:15:09,559 --> 00:15:13,939
Commander, I'm begging you, I really don't want to go.

189
00:15:15,120 --> 00:15:17,520
Let's go, Xiao Qiangzi.

190
00:15:19,679 --> 00:15:22,120
Thank you, Commander Yan.

191
00:15:23,279 --> 00:15:26,304
<i>[Civil and Military Strategies]</i>
You bad man, after all I've done for you.

192
00:15:26,304 --> 00:15:28,460
<i>[Phoenix Rite Palace]</i>

193
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:31,072
Your Majesty.

194
00:15:36,699 --> 00:15:41,480
I brought you here is actually because I need to ask you something.

195
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:43,939
Your Majesty, you flatter your servant too much.

196
00:15:43,939 --> 00:15:46,979
Considering your noble birth, and your beauty,

197
00:15:46,979 --> 00:15:48,540
not only does it bring nations to their knees,

198
00:15:48,540 --> 00:15:51,100
but also, your knowledge of poetry, music, chess, calligraphy, and painting.

199
00:15:51,100 --> 00:15:52,740
You excel in all of them.

200
00:15:52,740 --> 00:15:55,860
There's nothing from ancient to modern times, domestic or abroad, that you do not know.

201
00:15:55,860 --> 00:15:58,819
You have read more books than the meals I've had.

202
00:15:58,819 --> 00:16:00,679
If even you do not understand,

203
00:16:00,679 --> 00:16:03,880
then there's no one in this world who would.

204
00:16:05,260 --> 00:16:09,020
Indeed, my appearance is quite fine.

205
00:16:09,020 --> 00:16:12,620
But my knowledge is not as formidable as you describe.

206
00:16:12,620 --> 00:16:16,179
Be more honest, no flattering or fawning over your master.

207
00:16:16,860 --> 00:16:19,379
Miss Xue Ru, listen to what you are saying.

208
00:16:19,379 --> 00:16:22,140
Don't you think Her Majesty is beautiful?

209
00:16:22,140 --> 00:16:23,592
I…

210
00:16:26,579 --> 00:16:29,640
Tell me. What exactly is the method you used?

211
00:16:29,640 --> 00:16:32,779
Your Majesty, this is all a misunderstanding.

212
00:16:32,779 --> 00:16:34,620
I have no special talent.

213
00:16:34,620 --> 00:16:36,520
It's all due to HIs Majesty's approachability.

214
00:16:36,520 --> 00:16:38,120
How dare you talk back to Her Majesty.

215
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:39,940
Whatever you are told to do, you should just do it.

216
00:16:39,940 --> 00:16:43,240
Before dawn tomorrow, write down every method you know without missing a single one,

217
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:45,110
and present it to me.

218
00:16:45,760 --> 00:16:49,980
Your Majesty, I just arrived at the Phoenix Rite Palace and am not used to it.

219
00:16:49,980 --> 00:16:51,480
Finish it in one night, is that too…?

220
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:55,919
The task is too heavy. Can we slow down a bit?

221
00:16:58,519 --> 00:17:00,779
You do make some sense.

222
00:17:00,779 --> 00:17:03,600
In that case, not too many, 100 will do.

223
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:07,000
Remember to include illustrations with the text.

224
00:17:08,540 --> 00:17:10,556
Yes.

225
00:17:10,556 --> 00:17:12,716
<i>[Phoenix Rite Palace]</i>

226
00:17:57,459 --> 00:17:59,724
You scared me to death.

227
00:18:08,459 --> 00:18:10,140
Your Majesty,

228
00:18:10,140 --> 00:18:15,219
this is the secret manual I've worked on overnight for your review.

229
00:18:27,459 --> 00:18:30,236
This is good, turning from guest to host.

230
00:18:30,236 --> 00:18:32,300
Immediate results can be seen.

231
00:18:32,300 --> 00:18:34,540
I will go to try it out with His Majesty right away.

232
00:18:34,540 --> 00:18:38,120
Your Majesty, please don't act impulsively. What if it fails?

233
00:18:38,120 --> 00:18:42,379
Who knows if this is a trap meant to make Your Majesty fall out of favor?

234
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:45,000
It's not like that, Your Majesty.

235
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:46,839
I really didn't think that way.

236
00:18:46,839 --> 00:18:48,920
If Your Majesty does not believe,

237
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:51,720
then I will test it myself.

238
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:53,760
If it works, you can go then.

239
00:18:53,760 --> 00:18:56,199
Your Majesty, look! His true colors are finally showing.

240
00:18:56,199 --> 00:18:58,519
He just wants to take the opportunity to ingratiate himself with His Majesty.

241
00:18:58,519 --> 00:19:04,440
No, really, I didn't, Your Majesty.

242
00:19:04,440 --> 00:19:06,820
If you want to kill me, just say it.

243
00:19:06,820 --> 00:19:09,399
Stop torturing me.

244
00:19:10,759 --> 00:19:15,499
