247
00:19:28,340 --> 00:19:30,160
Hurry.

248
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:43,368
Gentle.

249
00:19:48,039 --> 00:19:54,220
<i>Changyun, it's me, Xiao Qiangzi.</i>

250
00:19:54,220 --> 00:19:56,960
Please open the door quickly.

251
00:19:59,599 --> 00:20:04,839
<i>Changyun, it's me. Open the door.</i>

252
00:20:05,540 --> 00:20:09,859
<i>Open the door, I'm here.</i>

253
00:20:11,240 --> 00:20:15,400
