254
00:20:20,319 --> 00:20:23,400
Don't be upset, one failure doesn't mean anything.

255
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:25,119
This turning from guest to host won't work.

256
00:20:25,119 --> 00:20:27,970
Let's just try another approach.

257
00:20:27,970 --> 00:20:29,350
Come on.

258
00:20:36,900 --> 00:20:39,820
I think this one is very good.

259
00:20:39,820 --> 00:20:42,000
